<title type="html"><![CDATA[From that which is specific to Tawheed al-Uluhiyyah]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="https://forum.salafiri.com/viewtopic.php?t=605&amp;p=647#p647"><![CDATA[
<strong><span style="color: #0000FF">Taken from: Tajreed at-Tawheed al-Mufeed for Imaam Taqee ad-Deen Ahmad ibn ‘Ali al-Magreezee (d.845 H) page 56:</span></strong><br /><br /><em>From that which is specific to al-Uluhiyyah:</em><br />The sujood, so those who prostrate for other than Him (Allaah) indeed have made comparison with Him And from it: at-Tawakil, so those who trust upon other than Him indeed made comparison with Him.<br /><br />And from it: at-Tawbah, so those who repent to other than him indeed made comparison with Him.<br /><br />And from it: the swearing with His (Great) Name; so those who swear by other than Him indeed made comparison with Him. And from it: the slaughtering for Him, so those who slaughter for other than Him indeed made comparison with Him.<br /><br />Translated by the poor servant of Allaah in most need of His Mercy and Forgiveness.<br /><em>Akhukum, Abu Abdul-Haadee Khaleel Davis</em><br /><br />Source: <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://loveforthesunnah.wordpress.com/2013/10/10/from-that-which-is-specific-to-tawheedul-uluhiyyah/">http://loveforthesunnah.wordpress.com/2 ... uluhiyyah/</a><!-- m --><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forum.salafiri.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=56">Shehzad Sattar</a> — Thu Nov 10, 2016 9:57 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
